        span Enter a URL to an online iCal file in the following screen and the data will be automatically synchronised with the HAT.

      div.plug-button-wrapper
        a.plug-button(href="/dataplug") Start Here
      div.plug-button-wrapper
        a.plug-button(href="/dataplug/details") Learn more about your data